---
title: Honey-Mustard Glazed Pork with Apple-Lentil Green Salad
description: An apple a day keeps the doctor away – at least that’s what they claim! With carrot, celery and lentils added to the mix, this dish is absolutely loaded with both flavour and nutrition. Now for the decadent part... we have taken the finest pork in the land and glazed it (generously) with the sweetness that only honey can pull off and the warmth of mustard. You are in for a treat!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-mustard-glazed-pork-c8102f16.jpg
